WEBVTT

00:18:34.278 --> 00:18:35.804
Perfino dai gruppi jihadisti.

00:18:35.828 --> 00:18:37.995
Riesco a farlo

00:18:37.995 --> 00:18:40.415
perchÃ© non mi metto
a litigare con loro,

00:18:40.415 --> 00:18:41.926
non mi infervoro,

00:18:41.950 --> 00:18:44.239
